Uttar Pradesh
Sep 09, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 13-year-old girl was allegedly raped here, following which one person has been arrested.

The incident took place last night when the victim had gone to the market under Revti Police Station area, Superintendent of Police R B Singh said, adding, the accused took her to a secluded spot and raped her.

An FIR was lodged against the youth on the complaint of the mother of the victim, following which he was arrested and sent to jail, the SP said.


